floorPlans.description:
This spacious, airy and stylish 1 bedroom urban loft has 9 foot ceilings, designer vinyl wood-plank flooring, contemporary cabinetry, quartz countertops, oversized stainless steel kitchen sink with disposal, GE stacked washer/dryer, state-of-the-art Samsung stainless steel kitchen appliances, ceiling fan, walk-in shower, air conditioning and heating, Google Fiber Webpass Internet & cable ready with lots of natural light. Fully furnished with new, high end furniture and all the living and kitchen amenities. Pets welcome! Minimum 30 day lease.
Enjoy the modern, open-space lifestyle of Nimitz Crossings' Urban Lofts in beautiful Point Loma/Ocean Beach. Embrace this walkable neighborhood located at the heart of the Voltaire Street Renaissance.
Walking distance to grocery stores, shopping and restaurants. Just minutes from Ocean Beach, Barnes Tennis Center, Robb Field, Mission Bay, Liberty Station, MCRD, Harbor Island and SD International Airport.

seoTags.description: Nimitz Crossing apartment community at 3909 Voltaire St San Diego CA, offers units from 660 - 807 sqft, a Pet-friendly, In-unit dryer, and In-unit washer. Explore availability.

description: Nimitz Crossing, the peninsula's newest luxury residences, offers stylish 1 bedroom urban lofts and bright & airy 2 bedroom, 2 ensuite bathroom homes. All units have new stainless steel appliances, designer cabinetry, quartz countertops, in-unit washer & dryers, vinyl plank flooring, secured parking, Amazon Hub lockers in lobby, elevator access to all floors, outdoor lounge with fireplace & BBQ, and pet relief area, all centrally located in the Ocean Beach/Point Loma coastal community. 1 mile to the sand, 5 minutes to the San Diego International Airport, Sunset Cliffs, Downtown Ocean Beach, SeaWorld and freeways, 10 minutes to Downtown and Balboa Park.
